Poynter is the quietest member of McFly, rarely speaking in interviews. His band mates often tease him about this, saying that he usually speaks without thinking, so it's much better that he stays silent. Although shy in press interviews, fans will know of Poynter's backstage antics and he is something of a fan favourite. In 2006, Poynter received the Virgin Award for "Most Fanciable Male."
